WEBVTT

00:07:57.880 --> 00:08:00.120
My law degree became my shield.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:03.256
My film partner became my husband.

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:05.416
(Laughter)

00:08:05.440 --> 00:08:06.640
I didn't expect that.

00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:12.976
And we became part
of a generation of advocates

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:15.960
working with communities
facing their own fires.

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:19.160
I worked inside of supermax prisons,

00:08:20.200 --> 00:08:22.256
on the shores of Guantanamo,

00:08:22.280 --> 00:08:23.736
at the sites of mass shootings

00:08:23.760 --> 00:08:25.880
when the blood
was still fresh on the ground.

00:08:27.200 --> 00:08:28.976
And every time,

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:31.496
for 15 years,